data.description: Welcome to this lovely home located on westside of San Antonio by Our Lady of the Lake University! This 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is the perfect fit for students or families looking for a comfortable and low-maintenance living space. Situated on a corner lot, this home offers both convenience and privacy.    Built just 5 years ago, this property boasts modern features and an updated interior. With low maintenance requirements, you can spend less time on upkeep and more time enjoying your new home.    Priced at $179,900, this house offers great value for its location and amenities. Whether you're a student looking for a convenient place to stay or a family searching for a cozy home, this property is worth considering.  If you have any further questions or would like to schedule a viewing, please don't hesitate to reach out.
